37:20.760 --> 37:22.370
Hold on a second.
Can we discuss this?

37:22.414 --> 37:24.633
My decision is final.

37:24.677 --> 37:26.766
Did you know about this?

37:26.809 --> 37:29.943
I'm sorry, Liam.
I tried to tell you...

37:29.986 --> 37:31.336
That RE/SYST was gonna
blow up a major city?

37:31.379 --> 37:32.859
That Nero could be ruthless.

37:32.902 --> 37:34.817
Yeah, well, so can I.

37:34.861 --> 37:36.166
Liam, wait.

37:36.210 --> 37:38.212
LIAM:
Listen up!

37:38.256 --> 37:39.431
I need everyone's attention!

37:41.084 --> 37:43.391
RE/SYST has learned

37:43.435 --> 37:46.568
the United States government
is building a giant rail gun.

37:46.612 --> 37:48.831
Now, combined
with our solar sail,

37:48.875 --> 37:52.835
we could actually knock Samson
off course and save the planet.

37:52.879 --> 37:54.533
Liam, don't do this.

37:54.576 --> 37:56.578
But RE/SYST would rather
threaten the lives

37:56.622 --> 37:59.842
of millions of people
than even entertain the idea

37:59.886 --> 38:02.410
of collaborating
with Darius Tanz.

38:02.454 --> 38:04.194
Now, if this is
the true face of RE/SYST,

38:04.238 --> 38:05.979
I will not be a part of it.

38:07.894 --> 38:10.853
I'm leaving.

38:10.897 --> 38:13.552
And I'm asking all of you
to come with me.

38:13.595 --> 38:15.858
Now, if you want to save the
planet, we need to walk out

38:15.902 --> 38:17.120
of here, right now.

38:18.861 --> 38:19.862
Right now.

38:25.041 --> 38:26.347
I'm ready to die
on the sword, Alycia.

38:37.750 --> 38:40.056
CROFT:
Liam.

38:40.100 --> 38:41.580
Hey, what are you doing? You're
gonna get yourself killed.

38:41.623 --> 38:43.886
