for a cause I believe in.

38:43.930 --> 38:45.714
Humanity!

38:51.633 --> 38:53.983
Oh, you're
gonna shoot me?

38:54.027 --> 38:55.376
Why? 'Cause
I disagree with you?

38:55.420 --> 38:57.465
Now who's the tyrant?

39:03.819 --> 39:06.953
Um, uh...

39:06.996 --> 39:08.911
I-I'm with Liam.

39:08.955 --> 39:10.435
You shoot him, you're gonna
have to shoot me, too.

39:19.574 --> 39:22.011
Well, I, uh, I guess
you're gonna have to shoot

39:22.055 --> 39:26.364
all of us, so good luck
with that asteroid.

39:40.769 --> 39:43.337
We're gonna do things
my way now.

39:50.083 --> 39:51.693
CROFT:
Okay.

39:51.737 --> 39:55.131
